WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 11=

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:26.480
Oh, right.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.310
This is for you.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.510
You're so thoughtful.

00:01:32.510 --> 00:01:33.430
I designed all of them.

00:01:33.430 --> 00:01:34.590
Not sure if you'll like it.

00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:37.200
I didn't get you anything.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.070
If you're interested,

00:01:38.070 --> 00:01:39.710
you can drop by my studio
anytime and pick one.

00:01:39.890 --> 00:01:41.280
There are plenty that suit you.

00:01:42.710 --> 00:01:43.950
Then I'll really come by.

00:01:43.950 --> 00:01:44.950
Deal.

00:01:47.150 --> 00:01:47.990
Mm.

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.070
Do you hang out with them often?

00:01:53.350 --> 00:01:54.430
Not really.

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:55.950
I've only met them two or three times.

00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:00.540
No wonder, the first time I saw you,

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:02.100
I knew you were different from them.

00:02:02.860 --> 00:02:03.900
How different?

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:07.380
People easily get influenced

00:02:07.380 --> 00:02:08.260
by a group's vibe.

00:02:08.460 --> 00:02:09.420
Stay too long,

00:02:09.620 --> 00:02:11.660
and you'll start adopting their mindset,

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:13.540
even

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:15.740
bad habits become normal.

00:02:17.100 --> 00:02:18.140
But I can tell,

00:02:18.780 --> 00:02:20.020
you haven't been shaped by them.

00:02:21.260 --> 00:02:22.500
We'll get along, I bet.

00:02:33.180 --> 00:02:34.380
Someone's getting married.

00:02:34.460 --> 00:02:35.340
Who?

00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:37.300
Who else? Use your brain!

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:39.220
Me and Sen?

00:02:39.220 --> 00:02:41.060
Not married. I said proposed.

00:02:41.350 --> 00:02:43.380
Aren't proposing and getting married
the same thing?

00:02:43.660 --> 00:02:44.900
What if she says no?

00:02:47.180 --> 00:02:49.220
Then propose again.

00:02:49.580 --> 00:02:51.100
You're so overthinking it.

00:02:51.300 --> 00:02:53.140
Be yourself. Just do it.

00:02:53.380 --> 00:02:55.100
You think proposing

00:02:55.460 --> 00:02:56.420
is a joke?

00:02:56.820 --> 00:02:57.860
What's actually going on?

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.660
I've been watching entertainment news
for 30 years.

00:02:59.660 --> 00:03:00.520
Never seen

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:01.820
a proposal fail.

00:03:01.820 --> 00:03:03.100
If they're still together,

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:04.660
they're heading for marriage anyway.

00:03:05.460 --> 00:03:07.460
Just wanna do that
unnecessary romantic stuff.

00:03:10.820 --> 00:03:12.300
I'll take your good wishes then.

00:03:12.300 --> 00:03:13.140
That's great news.

00:03:13.420 --> 00:03:14.300
Congrats.

00:03:14.700 --> 00:03:16.100
Come on, Zhazha Xiu.

00:03:16.700 --> 00:03:18.340
Don't you feel guilty saying that?

00:03:18.540 --> 00:03:19.460
What did I do now?

00:03:19.460 --> 00:03:20.860
Fine if others say it,

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:22.100
but you...

00:03:22.380 --> 00:03:23.540
We've seen

00:03:24.100 --> 00:03:25.340
your marriage.

00:03:26.220 --> 00:03:28.140
Your congrats sound like,

00:03:28.380 --> 00:03:30.860
"I've suffered for decades."

00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:33.100
"Finally another fool's falling in."

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.540
"A good path, but you won't take it."

00:03:34.540 --> 00:03:37.420
"Alright, come on in."

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:39.100
So I'm the exception.

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:40.500
The unluckiest one.

00:03:40.500 --> 00:03:41.980
One sign of maturity

00:03:42.940 --> 00:03:44.100
is realizing

00:03:44.100 --> 00:03:45.580
you're not that special.

00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:47.660
You're just one of the unlucky ones.

00:03:47.820 --> 00:03:49.660
Fine, you're right.

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:51.100
I'm just not that special.

00:03:51.420 --> 00:03:52.940
The second sign of maturity

00:03:53.420 --> 00:03:54.460
is confidence.

00:03:54.740 --> 00:03:56.100
What you need most right now

00:03:56.100 --> 00:03:57.460
is to stick to facts and reason.

00:03:57.660 --> 00:03:59.820
And prove you're the unluckiest.

00:03:59.980 --> 00:04:02.700
When a man openly talks about marriage,

00:04:02.700 --> 00:04:04.260
he's already not very manly.

00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:05.980
This isn't about masculinity.

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:07.100
You're just that...

00:04:07.940 --> 00:04:09.580
that rare kind of person.

00:04:11.460 --> 00:04:13.540
Someone that really sparks my curiosity.

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:14.940
That yin-yang head.

00:04:16.300 --> 00:04:18.140
Words, not fists.

00:04:18.140 --> 00:04:18.980
Xiu,

00:04:19.220 --> 00:04:20.540
why don't you just tell us?

00:04:20.540 --> 00:04:21.940
Think of it as giving me,

00:04:21.940 --> 00:04:24.500
someone about to get married,

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:26.180
a little brotherly advice.

00:04:26.180 --> 00:04:27.220
Exactly.

00:04:27.380 --> 00:04:29.460
How did your life
end up like this?

00:04:29.460 --> 00:04:31.580
Bei's dying to know.

00:04:31.580 --> 00:04:33.380
Can you talk normally?

00:04:33.860 --> 00:04:34.860
Let me ask you.

00:04:36.460 --> 00:04:38.540
When was the last time

00:04:38.740 --> 00:04:39.620
you went to the movies?

00:04:39.940 --> 00:04:40.780
Last weekend.

00:04:41.060 --> 00:04:42.100
Me too.

00:04:43.140 --> 00:04:44.410
But I didn't go with him.

00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:45.270
Don't get the wrong idea.

00:04:45.270 --> 00:04:46.420
Who'd want to go with you?

00:04:46.420 --> 00:04:47.740
- Encounter?
- I didn't even want to.

00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:50.060
You know when Yu and I

00:04:50.060 --> 00:04:51.780
last went to the movies?

00:04:53.060 --> 00:04:53.980
Five years ago.

00:04:54.940 --> 00:04:56.220
You're a simp?

00:04:56.440 --> 00:04:58.020
The training class
asked you to help out.

00:04:58.020 --> 00:04:59.580
The bar opening had you showing support.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:01.220
Now there's a baby's full-month party.

00:05:01.220 --> 00:05:02.500
They also want you to sing.

00:05:02.820 --> 00:05:04.820
You think you're a Z-list singer now?

00:05:04.980 --> 00:05:06.460
Watch your mouth, please?

00:05:06.620 --> 00:05:07.620
What do you mean by simp?

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:09.580
We're all buddies,
what's wrong with helping out?

00:05:10.460 --> 00:05:12.260
It's just their lousy buddy stuff.

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:13.140
And you always go.

00:05:13.140 --> 00:05:14.340
Why're you so desperate?

00:05:15.300 --> 00:05:16.140
Just wear this.

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:18.780
Do you have to be so mean?

00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:19.900
Sorry.

00:05:20.100 --> 00:05:21.380
I'm nice to everyone else.

00:05:21.470 --> 00:05:22.700
I don't need to act that way with you.

00:05:22.860 --> 00:05:24.420
Aren't you the one
who thinks I'm a shrew?

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:26.420
They pay me.

00:05:26.420 --> 00:05:27.980
Can't you even give me a smile?

00:05:27.980 --> 00:05:30.060
Thanks. How much do they pay you?

00:05:30.260 --> 00:05:31.460
I'll give you ten times that.

00:05:31.490 --> 00:05:32.340
With all this time,

00:05:32.350 --> 00:05:33.780
why not stay home
and focus on your music?

00:05:33.780 --> 00:05:34.940
Do I even have the time?

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:36.620
Don't you know where it goes?

00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:38.340
Those so‑called works of yours.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:39.620
Which one haven't I helped you with?

00:05:39.620 --> 00:05:41.300
Helping me is a waste of time.

00:05:41.300 --> 00:05:42.340
But why are you so eager

00:05:42.340 --> 00:05:43.620
to play simp for others?

00:05:44.580 --> 00:05:46.100
Can't wait to feed your ego?

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:47.260
Are you out of your mind?

00:05:47.260 --> 00:05:48.820
I said I'm not going! I'm so done.

00:05:48.820 --> 00:05:49.900
I must be crazy

00:05:49.900 --> 00:05:51.380
for dating a guy like you.

00:05:51.620 --> 00:05:52.460
Alright.

00:05:52.460 --> 00:05:53.900
I'll never meddle in your crap again.

00:05:54.180 --> 00:05:55.780
You deserve to be used.

00:05:56.260 --> 00:05:57.340
Freak.

00:06:01.700 --> 00:06:02.540
You coming or not?

00:06:02.740 --> 00:06:03.620
Where to?

00:06:03.620 --> 00:06:05.180
Forgot the movie tickets
we bought yesterday?

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:08.340
No off work.

00:06:08.940 --> 00:06:09.820
No fun.

00:06:10.900 --> 00:06:12.620
Only sleep about

00:06:13.060 --> 00:06:14.220
three or four hours a day.

00:06:15.180 --> 00:06:16.100
Eat,

00:06:16.100 --> 00:06:17.100
pee,

00:06:18.900 --> 00:06:21.660
even work when she's sick in bed.

00:06:22.180 --> 00:06:23.380
Honestly, I admire you.

00:06:24.380 --> 00:06:25.380
Bei told me

00:06:25.380 --> 00:06:27.300
you started with a few thousand yuan.

00:06:27.580 --> 00:06:29.420
Now you've got a team of dozens

00:06:29.420 --> 00:06:30.700
and your own brand.

00:06:31.380 --> 00:06:32.420
That's really impressive.

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:36.180
Just forced by life.

00:06:37.460 --> 00:06:39.660
I also wanna
study fashion design abroad.

00:06:40.060 --> 00:06:42.540
Be a carefree fashion designer.

00:06:42.540 --> 00:06:43.980
Not a clothing shop owner

00:06:43.980 --> 00:06:45.100
stuck working 24/7.

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:47.660
But this is how it is for now.

00:06:47.820 --> 00:06:49.300
She really is

00:06:50.140 --> 00:06:52.180
the craziest workaholic I've ever met.

00:06:56.020 --> 00:06:57.580
Why did you cut only the front pieces?

00:06:59.140 --> 00:07:00.020
Did I cut it wrong?

00:07:00.180 --> 00:07:01.070
Can you even do this?

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:01.970
It's such a simple task.

00:07:01.970 --> 00:07:03.580
Showed you a million times.
But still clueless.

00:07:03.580 --> 00:07:04.780
I'll redo it right away.

00:07:05.100 --> 00:07:05.990
Do you know how hard

00:07:05.990 --> 00:07:07.620
it was to find these fabrics?

00:07:08.420 --> 00:07:09.380
Please.

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:11.380
Can you just pay attention?

00:07:12.940 --> 00:07:14.540
When am I not paying attention?

00:07:16.420 --> 00:07:17.380
What's this?

00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:18.900
Do you think I'm blind?

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:20.660
If these could sell,

00:07:20.660 --> 00:07:21.780
I'd say nothing.

00:07:21.780 --> 00:07:23.180
But if I don't finish this order,

00:07:23.180 --> 00:07:24.860
no money.

00:07:24.860 --> 00:07:26.580
We won't make the mortgage
in two months, get it?

00:07:28.300 --> 00:07:29.420
If you don't want to do it,

00:07:30.100 --> 00:07:31.340
then get out of my way.

00:07:36.380 --> 00:07:37.740
When I'm with her now,

00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:39.220
I just feel inferior

00:07:39.850 --> 00:07:40.740
and ashamed.

00:07:40.740 --> 00:07:41.580
That's it.

00:07:41.860 --> 00:07:42.700
No matter how hard I try,

00:07:42.700 --> 00:07:44.140
I can't keep up with her.

00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:46.700
Before marriage, I had all these ideas.

00:07:47.380 --> 00:07:48.580
Ideal plans

00:07:48.820 --> 00:07:49.980
enough for a book.

00:07:51.100 --> 00:07:52.020
But after marriage?

00:07:53.660 --> 00:07:55.380
Drowned in loans.

00:07:56.180 --> 00:07:57.780
After paying
all the bills every month...

00:07:57.780 --> 00:07:58.620
Design sketch.

00:07:59.260 --> 00:08:00.940
I can't even afford a decent outfit.

00:08:01.660 --> 00:08:03.820
Every day I wonder
how to get through tomorrow.

00:08:05.660 --> 00:08:07.820
Poverty makes
all marital troubles worse.

00:08:08.980 --> 00:08:10.020
Back then, I thought,

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:12.540
if money can fix it,
then it's not a real problem.

00:08:13.580 --> 00:08:14.660
Just work harder to earn it.

00:08:16.660 --> 00:08:19.620
Movies, friend hangouts.

00:08:21.260 --> 00:08:22.420
Not even a thought.

00:08:25.660 --> 00:08:28.300
I said I was tired and wanted to sleep.

00:08:28.540 --> 00:08:29.500
But I didn't dare.

00:08:29.940 --> 00:08:30.940
I don't deserve it.

00:08:38.740 --> 00:08:39.980
These past few years

00:08:40.460 --> 00:08:42.260
should've been the best.

00:08:43.740 --> 00:08:45.460
But my life's been stagnant.

00:08:46.980 --> 00:08:47.820
Hopeless.

00:08:49.780 --> 00:08:50.660
So depressed.

00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:52.300
Then people changed.

00:08:53.980 --> 00:08:54.900
Maybe

00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:56.940
showed their true colors.

00:08:57.180 --> 00:08:59.780
I watched her go from a

00:09:00.540 --> 00:09:02.140
gentle woman

00:09:02.860 --> 00:09:04.140
to a

00:09:05.300 --> 00:09:07.260
cranky workaholic.

00:09:07.500 --> 00:09:09.540
We argued every single day.

00:09:10.020 --> 00:09:11.340
Before, he used to call me "Sis",

00:09:12.020 --> 00:09:13.660
then "Wife" after marriage.

00:09:14.420 --> 00:09:15.780
Now I'm like his Mom.

00:09:16.580 --> 00:09:17.860
Does he think I wanna be like this?

00:09:18.820 --> 00:09:20.260
She says I don't care about the family.

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:23.260
But every time she calls,

00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:25.820
I drop everything to help her.

00:09:26.340 --> 00:09:28.020
He still thinks he's doing me a favor.

00:09:28.460 --> 00:09:30.540
Not treating my problems as his own.

00:09:31.020 --> 00:09:32.420
Does he even know
what responsibility is?

00:09:33.100 --> 00:09:34.780
I have my own job too.

00:09:35.340 --> 00:09:37.020
I need to record songs
and arrange music.

00:09:37.580 --> 00:09:39.620
But I keep getting interrupted.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.260
When I was at my busiest,

00:09:41.260 --> 00:09:42.700
I didn't touch my guitar
for three months.

00:09:42.700 --> 00:09:43.700
Can you believe that?

00:09:44.110 --> 00:09:44.980
Who knows how much

00:09:44.980 --> 00:09:46.060
I've sacrificed?

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:47.780
Who else could do this?

00:09:47.940 --> 00:09:49.540
You're weighing her against your dream.

00:09:50.740 --> 00:09:51.740
But back then,

00:09:52.060 --> 00:09:53.300
wasn't she your dream too?

00:09:53.780 --> 00:09:54.860
Any possession

00:09:55.140 --> 00:09:56.460
comes with sacrifice.

00:09:57.220 --> 00:09:59.020
Some just can't let go,

00:09:59.300 --> 00:10:01.460
so they blame marriage,

00:10:01.620 --> 00:10:03.580
forgetting what they gained.

00:10:04.260 --> 00:10:05.540
I disagree.

00:10:06.660 --> 00:10:08.780
You can't put all eggs in one basket.

00:10:09.580 --> 00:10:11.100
If you don't get what music

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:12.540
means to a musician,

00:10:13.140 --> 00:10:14.220
you have no right to

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:15.900
ask him to give it up easily.

00:10:16.300 --> 00:10:17.980
If her career crashes,

00:10:19.220 --> 00:10:20.460
at least I can support us.

00:10:21.580 --> 00:10:23.220
Otherwise we'd starve.

00:10:23.460 --> 00:10:25.140
I don't wanna hold him back.

00:10:25.900 --> 00:10:27.260
But the endless chores

00:10:27.540 --> 00:10:29.100
and the overwhelming workload.

00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:31.100
I just can't handle it all on my own.

00:10:31.940 --> 00:10:32.780
Except for him.

00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:34.660
Who else can I really count on?

00:10:35.140 --> 00:10:36.340
I know she works hard.

00:10:36.820 --> 00:10:38.260
And she never complains.

00:10:38.980 --> 00:10:40.460
But I'm no expert at this.

00:10:41.620 --> 00:10:42.980
Switching from what I'm good at

00:10:42.980 --> 00:10:44.260
to what I'm not.

00:10:44.660 --> 00:10:46.100
Mistakes happen.

00:10:46.620 --> 00:10:48.380
Then she chews me out like I'm an idiot.

00:10:48.940 --> 00:10:50.020
It's not carelessness.

00:10:50.620 --> 00:10:51.820
He just doesn't care.

00:10:52.380 --> 00:10:54.100
He rejects doing anything for me.

00:10:54.420 --> 00:10:55.500
He thinks it's a favor.

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:56.820
Not his duty.

00:10:56.960 --> 00:10:58.100
So he thinks he shouldn't be blamed

00:10:58.300 --> 00:10:59.580
for mistakes.

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:01.900
I don't need this charity.

00:11:03.540 --> 00:11:04.940
Schopenhauer said,

00:11:05.380 --> 00:11:07.500
"Marriage cuts your rights in half,

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.770
and doubles your responsibilities."

00:11:09.220 --> 00:11:10.460
I think he was wrong.

00:11:11.020 --> 00:11:12.220
For you two,

00:11:12.620 --> 00:11:14.220
rights aren't just cut in half,

00:11:14.500 --> 00:11:16.140
and responsibilities
are more than doubled.

00:11:16.660 --> 00:11:17.660
In marriage,

00:11:18.540 --> 00:11:20.460
everyone carries responsibility.

00:11:28.340 --> 00:11:29.460
I often wonder,

00:11:31.100 --> 00:11:31.940
if over these years,

00:11:31.940 --> 00:11:33.420
I'd poured my energy into music,

00:11:34.060 --> 00:11:35.980
could I have earned enough money?

00:11:40.020 --> 00:11:41.980
I know he's not chasing fame or wealth,

00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:44.700
but he craves success deeply.

00:11:47.540 --> 00:11:49.340
I could've given her enough money.

00:11:49.900 --> 00:11:51.180
No more walking on eggshells.

00:11:51.980 --> 00:11:52.940
No more chains.

00:11:54.340 --> 00:11:55.260
Because of this,

00:11:55.980 --> 00:11:58.060
he used money and busyness
to brush me off.

00:11:58.060 --> 00:11:59.060
To avoid facing me.

00:12:00.700 --> 00:12:02.500
Do I really need a man like that?

00:12:08.780 --> 00:12:10.340
I still don't know

00:12:10.340 --> 00:12:11.740
what she wants.

00:12:12.540 --> 00:12:14.580
Must I degrade myself

00:12:14.580 --> 00:12:15.820
to be her worker?

00:12:16.020 --> 00:12:16.900
He just doesn't get

00:12:16.900 --> 00:12:18.060
what I care about.

00:12:19.940 --> 00:12:20.980
It's so simple.

00:12:21.820 --> 00:12:23.220
Among people our age,

00:12:23.460 --> 00:12:24.620
some are mature,

00:12:24.980 --> 00:12:27.020
while some are forever kids.

00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:29.420
But there's no right or wrong in that.

00:12:30.140 --> 00:12:31.420
The real issue now is...

00:12:31.660 --> 00:12:32.940
Just a bad fit.

00:12:34.900 --> 00:12:35.860
My dear,

00:12:36.460 --> 00:12:38.300
back then, I simply didn't understand.

00:12:40.300 --> 00:12:41.260
Now I finally know

00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:42.820
why I don't wanna marry.

00:12:42.820 --> 00:12:44.500
I'm scared of becoming like you.

00:12:44.700 --> 00:12:46.020
Hurting yourself and others.

00:12:46.700 --> 00:12:47.740
Come on.

00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:49.340
You're just scared

00:12:49.340 --> 00:12:50.940
you can't date
other girls after marriage.

00:12:52.060 --> 00:12:52.900
Fair point.

00:12:53.900 --> 00:12:54.740
Wait, today, you...

00:12:55.340 --> 00:12:56.340
You just admitted it?

00:12:56.340 --> 00:12:57.540
Let me say it again.

00:12:58.060 --> 00:12:58.940
I finally get

00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:00.220
why I resist marriage.

00:13:00.500 --> 00:13:01.820
I'm scared of becoming you

00:13:02.140 --> 00:13:04.180
and losing the chance
to date other girls.

00:13:06.540 --> 00:13:07.700
Wait, Bei.

00:13:08.780 --> 00:13:10.260
Don't we both

00:13:10.420 --> 00:13:12.740
know a girl named...

00:13:14.540 --> 00:13:15.940
Luanluan, right?

00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:22.820
Sorry

00:13:23.260 --> 00:13:24.580
for rambling.

00:13:25.580 --> 00:13:26.860
Hope you an Bei never

00:13:26.860 --> 00:13:28.020
end up like us.

00:13:28.900 --> 00:13:29.860
It's alright.

00:13:30.180 --> 00:13:31.540
I can already imagine

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:33.940
what marriage might bring.

00:13:34.780 --> 00:13:35.740
I think

00:13:35.740 --> 00:13:38.540
marriage is like boarding the same ship.

00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:40.940
Sometimes the direction clashes,
and the ship sinks.

00:13:41.380 --> 00:13:42.300
It happens.

00:13:42.940 --> 00:13:44.020
What scares me is

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:46.140
there's more than two on board.

00:13:47.340 --> 00:13:48.740
Then it's hard to say

00:13:49.460 --> 00:13:50.700
who drilled the hole.

00:13:55.020 --> 00:13:56.220
You're smart.

00:13:57.140 --> 00:13:58.900
You know I didn't

00:13:59.580 --> 00:14:01.100
call you here
just to vent.

00:14:03.300 --> 00:14:04.140
Go ahead.

00:14:06.940 --> 00:14:07.980
He cheated.

00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:11.020
She knows now.

00:14:15.620 --> 00:14:16.620
You came clean?

00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:18.220
I didn't.

00:14:18.460 --> 00:14:19.540
But that night at Linglong.

00:14:19.540 --> 00:14:20.820
Didn't you see it?

00:14:20.820 --> 00:14:22.300
Everything she said was sarcasm.

00:14:22.860 --> 00:14:23.780
She was harsh

00:14:24.020 --> 00:14:25.060
that day.

00:14:25.060 --> 00:14:26.300
But she wasn't just mocking you.

00:14:27.260 --> 00:14:28.220
Who else?

00:14:28.220 --> 00:14:29.100
Guess.

00:14:29.100 --> 00:14:31.300
But I was telling the truth.

00:14:31.500 --> 00:14:33.180
No way she was mocking me.

00:14:36.340 --> 00:14:38.180
It's all Zhazha Xiu's fault.

00:14:38.380 --> 00:14:39.700
Why don't we cut ties with him?

00:14:40.420 --> 00:14:41.460
Hey, bro.

00:14:41.740 --> 00:14:44.580
My mom said I can't play with wild kids.

00:14:47.940 --> 00:14:48.980
When did you figure it out?

00:14:49.660 --> 00:14:51.900
When a guy suddenly starts
showering every day,

00:14:51.900 --> 00:14:53.100
working out regularly,

00:14:53.540 --> 00:14:54.620
caring about his clothes,

00:14:55.100 --> 00:14:56.900
even creating with fire
like never before.

00:14:58.060 --> 00:14:59.420
How insensitive would I have to be

00:15:00.700 --> 00:15:01.780
to believe

00:15:03.300 --> 00:15:04.940
that behind all that glow and grind,

00:15:04.940 --> 00:15:06.740
there wasn't another woman?

00:15:10.340 --> 00:15:11.220
So, what's your plan?

00:15:11.500 --> 00:15:12.460
Kill them.

00:15:18.580 --> 00:15:20.140
Too bad that's against the law.

00:15:22.260 --> 00:15:23.140
True.

00:15:24.820 --> 00:15:25.980
Such a pity.

00:15:27.660 --> 00:15:29.660
Be honest with me.

00:15:30.300 --> 00:15:31.620
What is it you like about Luanluan?

00:15:34.900 --> 00:15:36.220
I like writing songs with her.

00:15:37.260 --> 00:15:38.980
Being with her

00:15:39.340 --> 00:15:42.020
feels so relaxing.

00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:44.660
Don't you notice she's always smiling?

00:15:45.460 --> 00:15:48.060
Always smiling,
always giving me approval.

00:15:48.340 --> 00:15:49.660
Always cheering me on.

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:51.940
No matter what happens,

00:15:51.940 --> 00:15:53.460
she says "it's okay."

00:15:55.420 --> 00:15:56.620
She makes me feel

00:15:57.060 --> 00:15:58.020
safe.

00:15:58.780 --> 00:15:59.980
Makes me feel

00:16:00.300 --> 00:16:02.900
like I can lean on her,
and she can lean on me.

00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:03.820
But... but

00:16:04.140 --> 00:16:05.380
the most important thing is

00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:07.260
I can

00:16:07.500 --> 00:16:08.900
only

00:16:10.500 --> 00:16:11.980
feel worthy when I'm with her.

00:16:13.020 --> 00:16:14.380
I feel alive.

00:16:15.420 --> 00:16:18.100
I could be better for her, but

00:16:20.140 --> 00:16:21.300
it turns out I was wrong.

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:25.420
Come.

00:16:25.980 --> 00:16:26.860
Right person.

00:16:27.380 --> 00:16:28.300
But the wrong relationship.

00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:32.660
Xiu.

00:16:34.020 --> 00:16:35.180
At this point,

00:16:35.420 --> 00:16:36.420
you know you messed up.

00:16:37.060 --> 00:16:38.300
You should cut your losses.

00:16:39.540 --> 00:16:40.540
Earlier,

00:16:40.820 --> 00:16:42.060
we never exposed you and Luanluan.

00:16:42.060 --> 00:16:43.220
We're partly to blame.

00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:44.660
But now that Yu knows,

00:16:45.380 --> 00:16:47.220
you need to talk to

00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:49.100
- Luanluan and...
- Hey, wait.

00:16:49.540 --> 00:16:50.500
Mind if I ask...

00:16:51.300 --> 00:16:52.220
Why Luanluan?

00:16:52.660 --> 00:16:53.580
Sorry.

00:16:53.580 --> 00:16:54.900
Only my best friend's feelings matter.

00:16:55.180 --> 00:16:56.020
I know.

00:16:56.030 --> 00:16:56.980
If it's your friend,

00:16:56.980 --> 00:16:58.140
even if he's cheating on his wife,

00:16:58.140 --> 00:16:59.300
you'll still let it slide.

00:17:02.220 --> 00:17:03.940
Come on, be a decent human, okay?

00:17:04.460 --> 00:17:06.540
What's wrong with following his heart?

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:08.020
This is not the time!

00:17:08.180 --> 00:17:09.020
Stop spouting your

00:17:09.030 --> 00:17:10.580
irresponsible nonsense, okay?

00:17:12.820 --> 00:17:13.740
Come here, come.

00:17:16.980 --> 00:17:18.820
Talk's fine. Hands off.

00:17:19.980 --> 00:17:21.020
Let me ask you.

00:17:21.580 --> 00:17:23.340
Who swore he loved Yu?

00:17:23.700 --> 00:17:24.980
Twenty years her parents raised her.

00:17:24.980 --> 00:17:26.180
Then let you marry her.

00:17:26.940 --> 00:17:28.180
And now she's facing these.

00:17:28.740 --> 00:17:29.580
Think carefully.

00:17:29.600 --> 00:17:30.900
Do you think what you've done is right?

00:17:32.180 --> 00:17:33.740
You tell us it's been hard on you.

00:17:33.800 --> 00:17:34.740
That you've lost so much.

00:17:34.750 --> 00:17:36.460
Lost this, lost your dreams.

00:17:36.820 --> 00:17:38.860
But Yu hasn't lost any
less than you have.

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:40.140
Daresay her bad temper

00:17:40.300 --> 00:17:41.980
has nothing to do with you?

00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:43.740
Life's hard.

00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:44.820
We're all just surviving.

00:17:45.060 --> 00:17:46.620
It makes people lose patience.

00:17:47.260 --> 00:17:48.100
But Xiu,

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:51.700
you're a man. Man up

00:17:51.980 --> 00:17:53.780
and fix this.

00:17:54.380 --> 00:17:56.380
No one forced you
to date or marry her, right?

00:17:56.580 --> 00:17:57.540
You chose this, right?

00:17:58.450 --> 00:17:59.300
Didn't you

00:17:59.300 --> 00:18:00.740
chase her like crazy?

00:18:00.740 --> 00:18:02.220
You told her "forever" at the wedding.

00:18:02.220 --> 00:18:03.080
We all heard it!

00:18:03.080 --> 00:18:04.180
Was that just empty talk?

00:18:04.820 --> 00:18:05.940
And now, look at you.

00:18:06.230 --> 00:18:07.980
You said you regret it.
You love someone else.

00:18:08.140 --> 00:18:09.820
You let Yu pay for your impulsiveness.

00:18:10.340 --> 00:18:11.540
If you keep this up,

00:18:11.940 --> 00:18:13.580
we're no longer brothers, alright?

00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.140
You're right.

00:18:26.100 --> 00:18:27.460
That's my glass.

00:18:31.300 --> 00:18:32.300
No manners.

00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:35.540
I'm yelling at you.

00:18:36.420 --> 00:18:37.700
But we're to blame too.

00:18:38.940 --> 00:18:40.220
We always thought we were friends with

00:18:40.220 --> 00:18:41.340
you and Luanluan.

00:18:41.580 --> 00:18:43.100
So we stayed out of it.

00:18:43.780 --> 00:18:45.300
But now things have gotten this far.

00:18:45.980 --> 00:18:47.820
You owe both women an explanation.

00:18:49.060 --> 00:18:50.020
Got it?

00:18:52.420 --> 00:18:53.860
Well, can I chime in?

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:55.260
I'm not sure if I should say it or not.

00:18:55.980 --> 00:18:56.900
If it's out of line,

00:18:57.180 --> 00:18:58.140
just ignore me.

00:18:58.540 --> 00:19:00.100
Doesn't it

00:19:00.780 --> 00:19:01.860
seem like

00:19:02.540 --> 00:19:03.700
Xiu doesn't have a choice here?

00:19:04.260 --> 00:19:05.540
You want me to get evidence?

00:19:06.020 --> 00:19:07.700
I know it's tough for you.

00:19:09.740 --> 00:19:11.100
But after thinking it through,

00:19:12.380 --> 00:19:14.060
you're the only one I can count on.

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:17.020
At this point, honestly,

00:19:17.500 --> 00:19:19.020
I really need a backup plan.

00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:21.100
No.

00:19:22.300 --> 00:19:23.180
That's not it.

00:19:24.380 --> 00:19:25.460
I'm doing this to...

00:19:27.060 --> 00:19:27.900
fulfill.

00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:29.380
Fulfill?

00:19:29.780 --> 00:19:30.620
Mm.

00:19:31.660 --> 00:19:33.780
Xiu seems really relaxed
when he's with you.

00:19:34.340 --> 00:19:35.660
I don't need anyone's fulfillment.

00:19:37.940 --> 00:19:39.020
Alright, I'll help you.

00:19:39.660 --> 00:19:40.500
Thanks.

00:19:42.150 --> 00:19:43.500
I knew I came to the right person.

00:19:45.340 --> 00:19:47.660
I just enjoy helping people
find happiness.

00:19:48.380 --> 00:19:50.420
I love seeing couples
get their happy ending.

00:19:51.460 --> 00:19:52.540
I'll send them on their way.

00:19:56.300 --> 00:19:57.540
To be honest, I was nervous

00:19:57.540 --> 00:19:58.660
when you asked me out.

00:19:58.940 --> 00:20:00.100
I feared you only talked to me

00:20:00.100 --> 00:20:01.140
because of Bei and others.

00:20:01.300 --> 00:20:02.980
Come on, why would I?

00:20:03.580 --> 00:20:04.780
A talented,

00:20:04.780 --> 00:20:05.940
and beautiful girl like you.

00:20:06.220 --> 00:20:07.260
Who wouldn't like you?

00:20:07.540 --> 00:20:08.940
You're the truly beautiful one.

00:20:09.340 --> 00:20:11.300
Since the first day I met you, I thought

00:20:11.540 --> 00:20:13.100
whoever's friends with you

00:20:13.260 --> 00:20:14.140
is so lucky.

00:20:14.340 --> 00:20:15.580
Aren't we already friends?

00:20:15.970 --> 00:20:16.820
If you say so,

00:20:16.820 --> 00:20:18.220
then what's left for me
to hesitate about?

00:20:19.420 --> 00:20:21.140
Drop by my café sometime.

00:20:21.420 --> 00:20:22.300
Sure.

00:20:22.300 --> 00:20:23.300
You own a café?

00:20:23.620 --> 00:20:24.980
Mm, and a flower shop too.

00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:26.260
Oh, right.

00:20:27.260 --> 00:20:28.940
I directed a play next weekend.

00:20:29.660 --> 00:20:30.820
You have to come and show support.

00:20:34.260 --> 00:20:35.100
I'll be there.

00:20:37.100 --> 00:20:39.220
(Play: "Delusion Girl",
written by Luanluan)

00:20:40.740 --> 00:20:41.580
Thank you.

00:20:41.960 --> 00:20:42.980
Congrats on opening, Mr. Sen!

00:20:42.980 --> 00:20:43.860
Thanks, thanks!

00:20:44.020 --> 00:20:45.900
Thanks everyone, thanks.

00:20:49.900 --> 00:20:51.100
Thank you.

00:20:51.740 --> 00:20:52.620
Thank you.

00:20:53.660 --> 00:20:55.940
One thing to clarify.

00:20:55.940 --> 00:20:58.580
This shop belongs to Mingming.

00:20:58.860 --> 00:21:01.060
I'm just Miss Ming's assistant.

00:21:01.660 --> 00:21:03.020
Hers is yours, huh?

00:21:03.020 --> 00:21:04.780
When are you two getting married?

00:21:04.900 --> 00:21:06.380
- Right?
- Yeah, right!

00:21:06.860 --> 00:21:07.940
Hey, Cao.

00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:10.300
You read my mind.

00:21:10.300 --> 00:21:11.340
I wanna hurry too,

00:21:11.340 --> 00:21:12.900
but I can't.

00:21:12.900 --> 00:21:14.660
I have to follow Miss Ming's plan.

00:21:17.300 --> 00:21:19.220
Honestly, we couldn't
have opened smoothly

00:21:19.380 --> 00:21:20.220
without

00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:21.140
our biggest investor,

00:21:21.380 --> 00:21:22.260
Mr. Bei.

00:21:22.260 --> 00:21:23.710
Mr. Bei, wanna say a few words?

00:21:25.460 --> 00:21:26.700
Mr. Bei!

00:21:26.700 --> 00:21:27.980
Don't say it.

00:21:28.380 --> 00:21:34.180
(Qian Chang)

00:21:34.180 --> 00:21:35.700
Fine, I'll say a couple words.

00:21:36.300 --> 00:21:37.980
So happy my good friend

00:21:38.180 --> 00:21:40.140
and former colleague

00:21:40.340 --> 00:21:42.140
are teaming up for this business.

00:21:42.540 --> 00:21:43.980
Hope they

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:45.900
stay together forever
and never let each other down.

00:21:46.150 --> 00:21:47.850
Good!

00:21:50.420 --> 00:21:51.580
Thanks, Bei.

00:21:52.060 --> 00:21:53.500
Bei, honestly,

00:21:53.900 --> 00:21:56.340
I kinda stole
your former employee like this,

00:21:56.500 --> 00:21:57.380
you don't mind, right?

00:21:58.020 --> 00:21:58.860
I do mind.

00:21:58.860 --> 00:21:59.780
Wanna give her back?

00:22:00.020 --> 00:22:00.940
No way.

00:22:02.180 --> 00:22:03.820
She's mine now.

00:22:05.460 --> 00:22:07.420
Alright, you two, enough.

00:22:07.580 --> 00:22:09.100
Do that at home.

00:22:09.100 --> 00:22:10.300
Exactly.

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:12.500
Remember a few years ago,

00:22:12.500 --> 00:22:13.700
you borrowed 500 yuan from me.

00:22:13.940 --> 00:22:14.820
I'm writing it off.

00:22:15.140 --> 00:22:16.840
Now I'm the second investor.

00:22:16.840 --> 00:22:17.700
Let me say a few words.

00:22:17.700 --> 00:22:18.560
Why are you everywhere?

00:22:18.570 --> 00:22:19.920
- Give me three hours.
- Security!

00:22:19.920 --> 00:22:20.800
Security!

00:22:20.800 --> 00:22:21.900
Get him out. Get him out.

00:22:25.700 --> 00:22:27.020
Come on, pass out the red envelopes!

00:22:36.860 --> 00:22:38.140
(Grand Opening)

00:22:38.140 --> 00:22:40.140
(Qian Chang, Photography Studio)

00:22:41.900 --> 00:22:43.500
You look extra special today.

00:22:53.740 --> 00:22:54.820
What about my outfit?

00:22:58.260 --> 00:22:59.100
Thanks.

00:23:00.620 --> 00:23:01.700
So cute.

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:04.140
I wondered how to pronounce

00:23:04.140 --> 00:23:05.820
these words when I came in.

00:23:06.060 --> 00:23:06.980
Photography?

00:23:08.980 --> 00:23:09.940
Sis.

00:23:10.860 --> 00:23:11.900
These two right here.

00:23:15.020 --> 00:23:15.900
Qian.

00:23:16.820 --> 00:23:17.660
Chang.

00:23:18.620 --> 00:23:19.860
They're from the Book of Songs.

00:23:20.660 --> 00:23:22.220
Oh.

00:23:22.220 --> 00:23:23.140
You're so cultured.

00:23:24.140 --> 00:23:24.980
What do they mean?

00:23:25.300 --> 00:23:27.780
Maybe it's the story
between Mingming and Sen.

00:23:31.100 --> 00:23:32.060
Don't mess with me.

00:23:34.420 --> 00:23:36.540
Do people nowadays love

00:23:36.540 --> 00:23:38.780
hiding secret meaning in names?

00:23:42.460 --> 00:23:43.700
I wanna get a fortune too.

00:23:46.100 --> 00:23:47.740
Feel free to ask him anything.

00:23:47.740 --> 00:23:48.900
He's our top salesperson.

00:23:50.260 --> 00:23:51.460
These few outdoor sets.

00:23:51.460 --> 00:23:52.940
I adore them so much.

00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:54.340
I see you paid

00:23:54.340 --> 00:23:55.780
a 100-yuan deposit online.

00:23:55.940 --> 00:23:58.500
That deposit can be converted to cash.

00:23:58.500 --> 00:23:59.380
Which means,

00:23:59.380 --> 00:24:00.740
on top of the 25% discount,

00:24:00.800 --> 00:24:01.980
you get an extra 500 yuan discount.

00:24:02.220 --> 00:24:03.060
I'll head over there.

00:24:03.460 --> 00:24:04.300
Okay.

00:24:04.460 --> 00:24:06.020
That's a great deal.

00:24:06.020 --> 00:24:06.860
Mm.

00:24:10.660 --> 00:24:11.500
Thanks.

00:24:19.140 --> 00:24:20.260
Thanks, Bei.

00:24:20.940 --> 00:24:21.780
No need to thank me.

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:22.900
You should thank Sen.

00:24:23.900 --> 00:24:25.860
Never thought he'd do this.

00:24:28.860 --> 00:24:30.020
Hope you truly love him.

00:24:33.300 --> 00:24:34.940
Only I know if I love him.

00:24:36.060 --> 00:24:37.220
I can't prove it.

00:24:37.540 --> 00:24:38.380
And I don't need to.

00:24:39.780 --> 00:24:41.260
Sen's done so much for you.

00:24:42.140 --> 00:24:43.140
Don't let him down.

00:24:44.580 --> 00:24:46.180
I'm in a relationship,
not making a deal.

00:24:46.780 --> 00:24:48.180
If we're really not a match,

00:24:48.380 --> 00:24:49.580
should we force it?

00:24:50.900 --> 00:24:51.820
Don't worry.

00:24:52.500 --> 00:24:54.620
Just treat it as if he borrowed
the money from you for me.

00:24:55.460 --> 00:24:56.300
I'll pay you back.

00:24:56.540 --> 00:24:57.620
It's not about the money.

00:24:58.020 --> 00:24:58.940
Why bring it up?

00:25:01.420 --> 00:25:02.340
How do you like it?

00:25:03.340 --> 00:25:04.900
We wanted to ask about this one.

00:25:05.340 --> 00:25:06.180
This package.

00:25:06.340 --> 00:25:07.180
Sure.

00:25:07.340 --> 00:25:08.620
I'm really curious.

00:25:09.700 --> 00:25:12.140
If one day Sen dumps me,

00:25:12.740 --> 00:25:13.740
what'll you do?

00:25:23.540 --> 00:25:24.620
I was right.

00:25:26.000 --> 00:25:27.580
You only care about who you care about..

00:25:28.900 --> 00:25:29.780
That's fine.

00:25:30.220 --> 00:25:31.660
I'm lucky to be your friend.

00:25:37.020 --> 00:25:38.300
That person must be Xiu, right?

00:25:46.460 --> 00:25:47.740
Xiu, Luanluan.

00:25:49.350 --> 00:25:50.340
- Finally met you.
- Grand opening.

00:25:50.340 --> 00:25:51.220
Grand opening.

00:25:51.340 --> 00:25:52.180
Thanks.

00:25:52.900 --> 00:25:54.140
Why didn't you sing the other day?

00:25:54.420 --> 00:25:55.980
Something came up last minute.

00:25:57.540 --> 00:25:59.020
If I didn't meet you today,

00:25:59.140 --> 00:26:00.660
I'd think Sen was lying.

00:26:00.940 --> 00:26:01.780
What did he say?

00:26:02.100 --> 00:26:03.260
That day he showed us

00:26:03.260 --> 00:26:04.700
a super pretty photo.

00:26:05.140 --> 00:26:06.300
None of us believed it.

00:26:07.220 --> 00:26:08.300
Now I see

00:26:08.300 --> 00:26:09.500
you're even more beautiful in person.

00:26:09.560 --> 00:26:10.980
Nah, I just know how to take photos.

00:26:11.460 --> 00:26:12.300
Since you're here,

00:26:12.300 --> 00:26:13.620
wanna take a photo to remember?

00:26:13.900 --> 00:26:15.220
No need, you're so busy today.

00:26:15.580 --> 00:26:16.660
Sen's here, so I'm not busy.

00:26:16.900 --> 00:26:17.860
Besides,

00:26:17.860 --> 00:26:19.740
the first photo of the opening
should be with friends.

00:26:20.100 --> 00:26:20.940
Let's do it.

00:26:21.660 --> 00:26:23.140
We rarely take photos together.

00:26:35.380 --> 00:26:37.460
Yuan, turn that light a bit that way.

00:26:38.900 --> 00:26:40.900
Okay, once the makeup artists are done,
we're ready.

00:26:42.980 --> 00:26:43.980
Ready.

00:26:45.980 --> 00:26:47.660
You two not close?

00:26:48.140 --> 00:26:49.340
Why sitting so far apart?

00:26:54.220 --> 00:26:55.500
Alright, let's try one shot first.

00:26:56.060 --> 00:26:57.860
Three, two, one.

00:27:00.980 --> 00:27:01.900
How about this.

00:27:01.900 --> 00:27:02.940
Let's make it a bit subtle.

00:27:03.380 --> 00:27:04.220
Luanluan.

00:27:04.380 --> 00:27:06.740
Face Xiu and lower your head a little.

00:27:07.820 --> 00:27:08.660
Xiu.

00:27:09.740 --> 00:27:10.580
Look at Luanluan.

00:27:13.620 --> 00:27:14.820
Alright, let's take one shot.

00:27:16.660 --> 00:27:17.500
Here we go.

00:27:18.180 --> 00:27:19.940
Three, two, one.

00:27:20.140 --> 00:27:21.940
Nice, okay, let's do another one.

00:27:22.580 --> 00:27:24.020
Three, two, one.

00:27:24.020 --> 00:27:25.460
Come on, get a bit closer.

00:27:26.060 --> 00:27:27.380
Three, two, one.

00:27:27.740 --> 00:27:29.100
Got it, now that's the vibe.

00:27:29.100 --> 00:27:30.660
Three, two, one.

00:27:32.980 --> 00:27:33.820
Luanluan.

00:27:34.260 --> 00:27:35.100
Mm.

00:27:35.820 --> 00:27:36.660
What's wrong?

00:27:39.660 --> 00:27:40.500
We...

00:27:51.340 --> 00:27:52.380
Don't tell me you can't say

00:27:52.380 --> 00:27:53.220
you're dumping me.

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:54.900
That's not it.

00:27:56.100 --> 00:27:57.100
Then what do you mean?

00:28:05.100 --> 00:28:06.140
You know me well.

00:28:07.140 --> 00:28:08.300
I'm not that hard to deal with.

00:28:10.580 --> 00:28:12.140
I know you don't stop liking me.

00:28:12.900 --> 00:28:14.500
You just can't be with me anymore.

00:28:16.580 --> 00:28:17.420
Right?

00:28:23.300 --> 00:28:24.140
I'm sorry.

00:28:25.180 --> 00:28:26.820
That's the last thing I wanna hear.

00:28:29.600 --> 00:28:30.940
I... I don't want to hold you back.

00:28:31.980 --> 00:28:34.260
Being with someone you love
is holding them back?

00:28:36.020 --> 00:28:37.900
Then I'd gladly
waste my whole life that way.

00:28:45.940 --> 00:28:46.900
It's okay.

00:28:48.100 --> 00:28:50.260
I'm happy for you going home. Really.

00:28:51.940 --> 00:28:52.780
Really.

00:28:56.900 --> 00:28:58.020
I'm such an idiot.

00:28:58.820 --> 00:28:59.740
I don't deserve you.

00:29:00.740 --> 00:29:02.300
I won't let you talk like that.

00:29:03.300 --> 00:29:04.580
You two are doing just fine.

00:29:12.940 --> 00:29:13.900
I don't wanna lose you.

00:29:14.340 --> 00:29:16.220
Then tell me what you expect me to do.

00:29:17.060 --> 00:29:19.060
So many times, I've thought about it.

00:29:19.620 --> 00:29:22.500
We should've ended this, but...

00:29:23.100 --> 00:29:24.700
But I still can't let you go.

00:29:24.700 --> 00:29:27.420
The thought of never seeing you again...

00:29:29.460 --> 00:29:31.860
So I just waited.

00:29:33.300 --> 00:29:35.860
As long as you stay silent,
I'll pretend everything's fine.

00:29:36.820 --> 00:29:38.740
Now you're really leaving.

00:29:42.500 --> 00:29:44.260
I knew, even if it wasn't today,

00:29:44.260 --> 00:29:45.940
this day would come sooner or later.

00:29:48.420 --> 00:29:49.860
Go on, then.

00:30:03.180 --> 00:30:05.100
Can you promise me one thing?

00:30:05.820 --> 00:30:06.660
Sure.

00:30:07.930 --> 00:30:09.140
You're agreeing without asking?

00:30:09.140 --> 00:30:10.700
Aren't you afraid
I'll ask you to divorce?

00:30:24.540 --> 00:30:25.740
You know I never would.

00:30:32.180 --> 00:30:33.580
Right now, I'm not in the right state

00:30:33.740 --> 00:30:35.620
for the upcoming shows.

00:30:38.860 --> 00:30:40.500
Can you stay with me for a few days?

00:30:41.300 --> 00:30:44.060
Let's pretend nothing happened tonight.

00:30:45.980 --> 00:30:47.540
After the play is over,

00:30:49.860 --> 00:30:51.100
let's break up then.

00:30:56.060 --> 00:30:56.900
Okay.

00:31:11.300 --> 00:31:12.260
Yeah, got it.

00:31:12.260 --> 00:31:13.140
Nice one.

00:31:14.300 --> 00:31:15.820
I'll print copies and send them to you.

00:31:20.220 --> 00:31:21.940
How did you deal with Yu and Xiu?

00:31:22.260 --> 00:31:23.300
I love Xiu.

00:31:26.100 --> 00:31:27.620
Maybe I'm just too narrow-minded.

00:31:27.900 --> 00:31:29.460
If someone I love

00:31:29.460 --> 00:31:31.380
sleeps with someone else every day,

00:31:32.540 --> 00:31:33.820
I couldn't possibly take it.

00:31:34.300 --> 00:31:35.780
They're the original couple.

00:31:36.140 --> 00:31:37.300
I'm just an extra.

00:31:38.060 --> 00:31:39.780
No right, so I gotta know my place.

00:31:40.700 --> 00:31:42.260
Unlike you,
who can complain

00:31:42.260 --> 00:31:43.660
they don't give enough

00:31:43.980 --> 00:31:44.980
or do enough.

00:31:46.740 --> 00:31:47.580
As for me,

00:31:47.580 --> 00:31:49.460
just being able to hang out
and talk with him

00:31:49.780 --> 00:31:50.740
already makes me happy.

00:31:56.860 --> 00:31:57.980
Don't you think that's too silly?

00:31:59.780 --> 00:32:01.020
I know you feel bad for me,

00:32:01.860 --> 00:32:03.980
but I have friends like you,

00:32:04.140 --> 00:32:05.340
and a man who truly loves me.

00:32:05.980 --> 00:32:07.220
I'm honestly already very lucky.

00:32:10.220 --> 00:32:11.060
Hey, don't move.

00:32:13.500 --> 00:32:14.660
Wipe your mouth.

00:32:18.980 --> 00:32:21.780
What if Yu finds out,

00:32:21.780 --> 00:32:23.260
and forces you to break up with Xiu...

00:32:23.260 --> 00:32:24.660
Can we really be
forced apart that easily?

00:32:27.860 --> 00:32:29.060
Is that what Xiu thinks too?

00:32:29.220 --> 00:32:30.940
Love can't be forced.

00:32:31.860 --> 00:32:33.940
You can't decide who you don't love,

00:32:34.420 --> 00:32:36.260
nor force someone to love you.

00:32:38.380 --> 00:32:39.980
You're really laid-back about this.

00:32:42.660 --> 00:32:44.460
Can I tell you the truth?

00:32:47.220 --> 00:32:48.460
If you really believe me,

00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:50.740
Xiu and I

00:32:52.020 --> 00:32:53.460
never crossed the line.

00:32:54.980 --> 00:32:55.820
What do you mean?

00:32:56.180 --> 00:32:57.300
I do love him,

00:32:59.900 --> 00:33:01.140
but our feelings are

00:33:01.340 --> 00:33:03.780
more like admiration.

00:33:05.140 --> 00:33:06.380
He feels the same way about me.

00:33:07.260 --> 00:33:09.100
Who wouldn't want to spend more time

00:33:09.260 --> 00:33:10.420
with someone they admire?

00:33:11.540 --> 00:33:13.060
Okay, he's married now.

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:14.780
But does marriage

00:33:14.900 --> 00:33:15.940
mean cutting off all contact

00:33:15.940 --> 00:33:16.900
with the opposite sex?

00:33:17.820 --> 00:33:18.940
Of course not.

00:33:18.940 --> 00:33:20.140
Easy for you

00:33:20.300 --> 00:33:21.300
to say from my side.

00:33:22.500 --> 00:33:23.420
What if

00:33:23.700 --> 00:33:26.220
Bei had a "Luanluan" around?

00:33:26.900 --> 00:33:28.100
Will you still be happy?

00:33:35.700 --> 00:33:37.220
If they're really innocent...

00:33:37.320 --> 00:33:38.540
That's where the problem lies.

00:33:38.980 --> 00:33:40.220
How can you be so sure

00:33:40.380 --> 00:33:41.620
they're actually innocent?

00:33:43.780 --> 00:33:45.780
All soulmate or confidant

00:33:46.380 --> 00:33:48.100
through their partner's eyes,

00:33:48.400 --> 00:33:49.700
always seem a bit suspicious, right?

00:33:53.180 --> 00:33:54.540
But you and Xiu.

00:33:56.340 --> 00:33:57.620
You're really not lovers?

00:33:57.820 --> 00:33:59.340
Wasn't Jiang Yifan also Gong's lover?

00:34:12.740 --> 00:34:13.780
Don't worry.

00:34:15.060 --> 00:34:16.380
Gong didn't tell me anything.

00:34:17.100 --> 00:34:17.980
I just happened to

00:34:17.980 --> 00:34:19.700
see that street interview video
of you two.

00:34:20.460 --> 00:34:22.180
That's when I realized
you were Jiang Yifan.

00:34:31.180 --> 00:34:32.180
Did you ever love him?

00:34:32.660 --> 00:34:33.500
No.

00:34:35.540 --> 00:34:36.420
I believe you.

00:34:44.220 --> 00:34:45.340
I know what you're thinking.

00:34:45.980 --> 00:34:46.820
Don't worry.

00:34:46.820 --> 00:34:47.940
I won't tell anyone.

00:34:49.420 --> 00:34:50.380
I'm not that low.

00:34:50.660 --> 00:34:51.580
I trust you too.

00:34:54.540 --> 00:34:56.220
I believe you and Xiu are innocent.

00:34:57.060 --> 00:34:58.580
So when you said
you wanted to be friends,

00:34:58.600 --> 00:34:59.580
you weren't lying, right?

00:35:00.340 --> 00:35:01.340
Of course not.

00:35:01.940 --> 00:35:03.860
Sometimes things bottled up for so long.

00:35:04.340 --> 00:35:05.700
You need someone to talk to.

00:35:06.380 --> 00:35:07.380
Now I have you.

00:35:08.220 --> 00:35:09.180
I couldn't be happier.

00:35:10.140 --> 00:35:11.180
(Share)

00:35:11.260 --> 00:35:12.100
That's great.

00:35:12.100 --> 00:35:13.100
(Send to friend)

00:35:15.140 --> 00:35:17.380
(Yu)

00:35:21.260 --> 00:35:22.260
You're sending this to Yu?

00:35:24.100 --> 00:35:24.940
Yeah.

00:35:25.580 --> 00:35:26.420
Is that not okay?

00:35:26.960 --> 00:35:28.420
Maybe… maybe don't send it.

00:35:29.580 --> 00:35:30.420
Why?

00:35:32.740 --> 00:35:33.980
This needs to be sent to...

00:35:38.460 --> 00:35:39.300
You scared me.

00:35:39.320 --> 00:35:40.860
Are you out of your mind?

00:35:42.420 --> 00:35:43.620
What are you two doing?

00:35:44.820 --> 00:35:45.900
None of your business.

00:35:46.620 --> 00:35:47.660
Cut the PDA.

00:35:48.660 --> 00:35:49.580
Sen's gorgeous wife

00:35:49.580 --> 00:35:51.020
wants you to take a promo photo.

00:35:51.020 --> 00:35:51.860
Hurry over.

00:35:52.740 --> 00:35:53.580
Maybe not.

00:35:53.710 --> 00:35:54.580
Yeah.

00:35:54.580 --> 00:35:55.860
Why not?

00:35:56.140 --> 00:35:57.580
You think everyone's like me,

00:35:57.580 --> 00:35:59.220
trying to please you two
even when you act cold?

00:36:00.300 --> 00:36:01.140
Besides,

00:36:05.720 --> 00:36:07.100
she already picked out the clothes.

00:36:13.700 --> 00:36:14.540
Then let's go.

00:36:17.500 --> 00:36:18.460
You picked this for me?

00:36:18.900 --> 00:36:19.740
She asked me to.

00:36:20.220 --> 00:36:21.060
It suits you.

00:36:21.500 --> 00:36:22.340
It suits me.

00:36:23.740 --> 00:36:24.620
Fine, head out.

00:36:24.620 --> 00:36:25.460
Don't film this.

00:36:25.460 --> 00:36:26.340
Why not?

00:36:26.700 --> 00:36:27.580
What do you mean, why not?

00:36:27.580 --> 00:36:28.780
Is it appropriate for you to be here?

00:36:28.940 --> 00:36:30.060
Why wouldn't I?

00:36:30.700 --> 00:36:31.940
Just stole a little of your spotlight.

00:36:31.950 --> 00:36:32.830
Besides,

00:36:32.850 --> 00:36:34.580
I picked the outfit
and did all the work.

00:36:34.900 --> 00:36:36.140
I deserve some credit, right?

00:36:36.140 --> 00:36:37.300
- I don't care. I'm taking it.
- Wait, you...

00:36:37.300 --> 00:36:38.460
Fine, let's all take it together.

00:36:39.420 --> 00:36:40.340
See?

00:36:40.700 --> 00:36:41.980
- So generous.
- That...

00:36:42.420 --> 00:36:43.820
Just pretend you don't see him.

00:36:46.340 --> 00:36:47.340
You ready?

00:36:47.980 --> 00:36:48.820
Mm.

00:36:51.620 --> 00:36:54.020
Three, two, one.

00:37:20.580 --> 00:37:21.420
(Bei)
(You home?)

00:37:24.420 --> 00:37:25.260
(Xiaoxi)
(Not home.)

00:37:25.800 --> 00:37:27.060
(Bei)
(Wanted to talk to you.)

00:37:27.660 --> 00:37:28.620
Xiaoxi.

00:37:44.700 --> 00:37:45.660
Miss Chen.

00:37:47.580 --> 00:37:49.220
I thought you'd blow me off.

00:37:49.660 --> 00:37:50.580
I'll grab some popcorn.

00:37:50.860 --> 00:37:52.740
Can't watch a movie without it.

00:37:53.140 --> 00:37:54.020
Thanks.

00:37:55.460 --> 00:37:57.260
Dr. Lin, why do so many people

00:37:57.420 --> 00:37:59.220
date at the movies?

00:38:00.020 --> 00:38:01.020
The dark effect.

00:38:01.940 --> 00:38:03.660
In dim light, people

00:38:03.900 --> 00:38:05.740
lower their guard and feel safer.

00:38:06.180 --> 00:38:07.620
The chance of getting close

00:38:07.620 --> 00:38:09.220
is much higher
than in bright places.

00:38:10.820 --> 00:38:11.860
Do you think it works?

00:38:13.460 --> 00:38:14.340
I hope it does.

00:38:14.940 --> 00:38:16.860
So our talk will be more relaxed.

00:38:18.060 --> 00:38:19.140
I'm looking forward to it.

00:38:19.620 --> 00:38:20.820
Come on, the movie's starting.

00:38:20.820 --> 00:38:21.660
Mm.

