♪Take my hand again♪

00:39:03.640 --> 00:39:05.399
♪Take my mind again♪

00:39:05.480 --> 00:39:08.839
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:39:09.240 --> 00:39:11.417
♪I'm falling out again♪

